Q-  What did you do when you needed to motivate a group of individuals or promote collaboration on a particular project?
Ans This happened to me during SAP project, we were group of 4 people from 4 different state, we just do work and some formal talk and
    then leave for the day. I realised that we should know each other more as this will increase thier involvement and performance 
    and they will happily come to do their work and leave at the end of the day, so twice in a day i just try to learn more about them
    and always try to start conversation which involves everyone. And with in a week i realised we are moving forward rapidly
 
Q:  How have you leveraged data to develop a strategy?
Ans I realised the power of data little late, but eventually i do.
    I want to mention that apart from my job i also have my own you tube channel where i play some famous somgs of Indian and some
    hollywood songs in fingerstyle guitar and giving a lesson for my covers also.
    I take decision about which song should i cover next, based on available data like searching volume, how popular song is,
    experimenting on searching.
    in addition to do that , i also used google analytics where i store my audience data 
    
    
    apart from that when i realised the value of data, i used to store the value of my money spendings like how much did i spent on
    eatings, on myself, on vehicle petrol and all these types of things and see which thing should i do it in more efficient and
    with less money.
    So for e.g. i noticed that i spend a lot of money on unnecessary things, 
    i categorise things and take an action according to the need only.
